metadata.title: Primitives By Kathy Free Spirit String Art Box Sign
features: FUN BOHO STYLE: Lightly stained and distressed slat wood sign featuring bright, feather themed string art brings a bit of hippie chic to your living room, office, bedroom or baby nursey.

EXPRESS YOUR WILD SIDE: Personalize your home with bohemian style with this simple yet impressive wall art. It is the perfect size for adding character to almost any room in your home or office. Sign measures 5 inches wide by 15 inches high.

A THOUGHTFUL PRESENT: Whether given as a birthday, baby shower, graduation, or house warming present, this modern farmhouse wall decor is touching and memorable. Reclaimed wood with primitive style sanding on surfaces and hand sanded edges makes each sign unique.
ON TREND HANDMADE STRING ART: Rustic, shiplap wood and colorful string artwork will brighten your home, office, or bedroom with its folksy, warm style.

EASY TO DISPLAY: Box signs are specially designed to freely stand on their own or hang on the wall for flexibility to place anywhere you prefer. It is a fun way to brighten up a hallway, family room, or entryway.
description: A vertical slat wood box sign featuring a hand-strung, multicolored feather design with hand lettered "Free Spirit" sentiment. Easy to hang or can free-stand alone.
